question.query: what assets (over $50k in 30d revenue) have had the highest growth in revenue in the last 30 days

agentResult.finalAnswer:
![](https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjriemfd/image/upload/v1768254337/veldt/eblfkznko43bzngsyqoz.jpg)

**Highest revenue growers (last 30d) with ≥$50k revenue in the last 30d** — using the strongest 30d growth signals available in the dataset (some are measured as **30d % change**, some as **WoW** but still indicative of 30d acceleration).

- **GMGN (Telegram Bot)** — **+1645% MoM** on app revenue (chart data), and it’s already doing **~$1.73M 30d revenue** on the revenue table snapshot. This is the cleanest “highest growth” print in the data with the threshold satisfied.
- **Hyperliquid (Derivatives)** — **+309.65% MoM** on daily app revenue (chart data). Absolute scale is massive (**~$75M–$95M 30d revenue** depending on snapshot), but growth still screens top-tier.
- **Jupiter (Solana, Derivatives/Aggregator)** — **+399.16% MoM** on daily app revenue (chart data) and **~$13.1M–$26.7M 30d revenue** depending on snapshot/table.
- **four.meme (Launchpad)** — **+438.74% MoM** on daily app revenue (chart data). Clears the $50k bar trivially (daily revenue alone is **~$608k** on that chart readout).
- **Pump.fun (Launchpad)** — **+93.27% MoM** on daily app revenue (chart data) with **~$32M–$36M 30d revenue** in the tables.
- **Polygon (Chain/L2)** — **~+190%** growth on revenue in the recent movers leaderboard and separately referenced as **~+196%** onchain revenue growth.
- **Internet Computer (Chain/L1)** — appears on the weekly revenue-growth leaderboard with **~$59.8K 7d revenue (+164%)**, which annualizes to **>$50k 30d** if sustained.

This list is biased toward assets where the feed includes explicit **MoM growth** (best) or high-signal recent growth leaderboards. The biggest “pure growth” winner in the data is **GMGN**, with **Hyperliquid/Jupiter/four.meme** next tier on MoM prints.
